Some people do yard work on the weekend not me . I worked with 2 new models this weekend and another very experienced model . I love working with new talent & hope they truly never lose the quality of greatness they had this weekend . 
1. They were so thankful for their team and said it several times . 
2. The willingness to learn all information the team was giving . 
3. They trusted the process and they were confident in themselves. 
4. They allow the team to create the vision they had . 

Thanks for reminding me the reason I started this business over 30 years ago . 

@dhdhbec

These words we have all felt at some point as a artist. When another person tries to put value on your talent by their opinion but I have learned that the opinion of others doesn’t measure anyone’s value . We all have worth & don’t need anyone to confirm it . I stop wasting my time trying to prove it , depending on someone else to measure it . The key is to know we can always reinvent our self’s allowing our creativity to lead the way . I am constantly learning, working towards the person I want to be without degrading another artist to get there. I can still be successful when someone else got the job, or become the #1 . My value is set by me not how much I am working but practicing being content with every situation. I am a artist that can reinvent myself at anytime. Be kind to yourself and support other artist success .
